cast.overview: Maleficent and her goddaughter Aurora begin to question the complex family ties that bind them as they are pulled in different directions by impending nuptials, unexpected allies, and dark new forces at play.
cast.title: Maleficent: Mistress of Evil

details.biography:
John Lebar is a British actor known for his giant stature; standing at 7 feet 3 inches (2.21 m).

In 2007 he starred as a plague doctor in The Sick House.

Lebar portrays one of the Space Jockey aliens seen in Ridley Scott's 2012 science fiction film, Prometheus.
details.name: John Lebar
